B\subset \mathbb{R}
B\subset\mathbb{R}^2
B = \{(x,y)\,\,|\,\, x+y < 1 \,\,;\,\, x,y>0\}
 P(X\in B) = \int_B f_X(x)dx,
  P((X,Y)\in B) = \iint_B f_{(X,Y)}(x,y)dxdy. 
 P(X+Y<1) = \int_{0}^{1}\int_{0}^{1-y} f_{(X,Y)}(x,y)dxdy.
